OL,3,CMotorists warned after thousands
OL,4,Ctargeted by 'cash for crash' moped
OL,5,Cscammers
OL,7,FScammers on mopeds are deliberately
OL,8,Fcrashing into other vehicles to make
OL,9,Fbogus insurance claims, motorists have
OL,10,Fbeen warned.
OL,12,FMore than 4,000 people have been
OL,13,Ftargeted by a "crash for cash" moped
OL,14,Fscam in the past three years, after an
OL,15,Fanalysis of fraudulent claims received
OL,16,Fby 21 insurers.
