OL,3,CMotorists warned after thousands
OL,4,Ctargeted by 'cash for crash' moped
OL,5,Cscammers
OL,7,FPeople in London are being
OL,8,Fparticularly targeted but scammers
OL,9,Fcould strike in other parts of the UK
OL,10,Fwhere road users may be less aware of
OL,11,Fthe issue, motorists have been warned.
OL,13,FThe fraudsters often intimidate
OL,14,Fvictims to try to get them to admit
OL,15,Ffault in a collision.
OL,17,FIn some recent cases, instead of
OL,18,Fmaking a claim they try to pressure
OL,19,Fvictims into handing over cash. Those
OL,20,Fconsidered to be more vulnerable are
OL,21,Fmore likely to be targeted.
