OL,4,Ctargeted by 'cash for crash' moped
OL,5,Cscammers
OL,7,FThe growing trend is being
OL,8,Finvestigated by the Insurance Fraud
OL,9,FBureau (IFB) and City of London
OL,10,FPolice's Insurance Fraud Enforcement
OL,11,FDepartment (IFED) alongside the
OL,12,Finsurance industry.
OL,14,FUrsula Jallow, director at the IFB,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Thousands of people have been
OL,16,Ftargeted, and these shameless
OL,17,Fscammers' tactics are becoming
OL,18,Fincreasingly aggressive. For instance,
OL,19,Fwe've found women who are driving
OL,20,Falone or with their children are being
OL,21,Ftargeted more."
