OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Tom Hill,
OL,8,Ffrom City of London Police's IFED,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The value of the claims that
OL,10,Fcan be lodged for repairs, personal
OL,11,Finjury and replacement vehicles makes
OL,12,Fthis an incredibly lucrative
OL,13,Fopportunity for fraudsters."
OL,15,FHe added: "If you witness or are
OL,16,Finvolved in a collision and suspect it
OL,17,Fis crash for cash fraud, gather as
OL,18,Fmuch information as possible.
