OL,7,F"This could be the make and model of
OL,8,Fthe moped, its number plate or the
OL,9,Fclothing that the driver is wearing.
OL,10,FThese details could be invaluable in
OL,11,Fdisproving a fraudulent claim. Report
OL,12,Fthe incident as soon as possible to
OL,13,Fthe Insurance Fraud Bureau's
OL,14,FCheatLine."
