OL,3,CMotorists warned after thousands
OL,4,Ctargeted by 'cash for crash' moped
OL,5,Cscammers
OL,7,F3. Many moped scammers work with an
OL,8,Faccomplice to act as a witness and
OL,9,Fhelp facilitate the fraud. They may
OL,10,Falso use a van to obscure the victim's
OL,11,Fview.
OL,13,F4. If someone is targeted, collect as
OL,14,Fmuch information about the incident as
OL,15,Fpossible, including details of the
OL,16,Fother road user, any witnesses,
OL,17,Fphotographs and recordings (local CCTV
OL,18,For dashcam footage).
