OL,7,F5. If someone thinks they have been
OL,8,Ftargeted, they should tell their
OL,9,Finsurer and contact their local police
OL,10,Fforce. Evidence of the scam can be
OL,11,Freported to IFB's confidential
OL,12,FCheatLine service on an online form,
OL,13,For the phone line powered by
OL,14,FCrimeStoppers at 0800 422 0421.
